# Saturn

Marketing website for **Saturn** — a fast, elegant RSS reader for iPhone, iPad, and Mac.

Built with [Next.js](https://nextjs.org) (App Router) and deployed on [Vercel](https://vercel.com).

## Pages

- `/` — Hero section with the "Download on the App Store" button and feature highlights
- `/privacy` — Privacy Policy
- `/terms` — Terms of Service

## Development

```bash
npm install
npm run dev      # http://localhost:3000
npm run build    # production build
```

## Configuration

Site-wide values (app name, App Store URL, contact email, legal "last updated"
date) live in [`lib/site.ts`](./lib/site.ts). Update the placeholder
`appStoreUrl` there once the app is live on the App Store.

## Deployment

This repo is linked to a Vercel project. Vercel auto-detects Next.js — no extra
configuration is needed. Pushes to the connected branch trigger a deployment.
